  when T.CHANNEL_ID is null then UPPER($SQ$UNKOWN$SQ$)    else T.CHANNEL_ID   end as CHANNEL_ID,   T.PROCESS_TYPE,   T.TENANT_ID,   T.UETR,   T.npsst_id,   T.VALUE_DATE,   T.CDTR_IBAN, cbuae_return_code is not null    and process_name not in ($SQ$Receive pacs004$SQ$) then $SQ$Accepted by Bene Bank$SQ$    when response_code = UPPER($SQ$RJCT$SQ$)    and cbuae_return_code is not null then $SQ$Rejected by Bene$SQ$    when pl.status in (UPPER($SQ$OP_P2P_POSTING_SUCCESS$SQ$), UPPER($SQ$OP_P2B_FUND_AUTHORIZED$SQ$)) then $SQ$Posting Completed$SQ$    when t.process_status in ($SQ$RCTCompleted$SQ$, $SQ$RCTReturned$SQ$)    and pl.process_name = $SQ$Place Pacs008$SQ$ then $SQ$Send to CB$SQ$    when pl.status in (UPPER($SQ$OP_AC_STATUS_ACCEPTED$SQ$),
